[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0967","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0967.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0648","title":"通用 X.25 服务运行配置问题（此编号已废弃，不构成安全漏洞）","description":"tags.<value>CVE-1999-0648 候选编号已被驳回，原因为该条目描述的是\"X25 服务正在运行\"这一系统配置状态，并非直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷类型。此类配置类问题更适合收录于通用配置枚举（CCE）体系。该候选编号不应被用于安全漏洞追踪，其 CVSS 评分为 0，不具备实际可利用的攻击条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0648"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.170","remediation":"如非必要，建议在系统配置中禁用 X.25 服务（如 Solaris 中停止 x25 相关 daemon，Linux 中移除或封锁 x25 内核模块），或在网络边界防火墙封禁 TCP 端口 2000/2001 以限制外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0648","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0967.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0966","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0966.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0647","title":"UNIX bootparamd 服务运行配置问题","description":"bootparamd（引导参数服务）是一种基于 RPC 的传统网络服务，用于向无盘客户端提供引导参数。该服务运行于系统中时，可能被远程攻击者利用来探测网络配置与主机信息，造成信息泄露。由于其本身不直接引入安全漏洞，更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理。建议在非必要环境中禁用该服务以减少攻击面。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0647"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.137","remediation":"建议在服务器上禁用 bootparamd 服务，该服务用于无盘工作站启动，在现代网络中已无必要且可能泄露系统信息。执行 `killall bootparamd` 并禁止随系统启动（删除或注释相关 inetd 条目）。若确实需要，应在防火墙中限制 RPC 端口 (111/udp) 仅允许受信任子网访问，或配置 hosts.allow/hosts.deny 进行访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0647","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000468.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/1b758e4b71978ff973a6df1bc69fc70b932735fb/advisories/2000/02/EUVD-1999-0630.json","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0966.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0965","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0965.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0646","title":"LDAP 服务配置暴露风险","description":"CVE-1999-0646 已被撤销（REJECTED），不再作为安全漏洞使用。该候选编号的原始描述为 LDAP 服务正在运行，仅涉及 LDAP 协议服务的配置暴露情况，并非直接的安全漏洞，不满足 CVE 漏洞收录标准。NVD 官方说明指出该条目更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系进行管理，因此该编号已被废弃。此条目不涉及任何可利用的安全缺陷，不存在攻击条件或利用方式。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0646"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.103","remediation":"如非业务必需，建议禁用 LDAP 匿名绑定，配置 LDAPS（LDAP over SSL/TLS）代替明文 LDAP（端口 389），并在防火墙层面限制只有信任网络可访问 LDAP 端口（389/636）。同时启用访问控制列表（ACL）和账户密码策略，防止信息泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0646","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0965.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0964","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0964.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0645","title":"IRC 服务运行信息泄露漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0645 已被拒绝使用，原分配描述为\"IRC 服务正在运行\"，该条目实质描述的是系统中 IRC 服务处于启用状态的配置信息，而非本身存在安全漏洞。由于此类配置枚举更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系，NVD 已将其标记为 REJECT 状态。系统管理员应关注 IRC 服务是否确实需要运行，若无需使用建议关闭以减小攻击面。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0645"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.070","remediation":"在服务器上禁用不必要的 IRC 服务。Linux 系统执行 systemctl disable ircd 并停止对应服务；Windows 系统通过 services.msc 将 IRC 相关服务设为禁用。在边界防火墙上封禁 IRC 默认端口 6660-6669/TCP 的出站流量，防止内网主机外连 IRC 服务器。定期使用端口扫描确认 6660-6669 端口无对外开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0645","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0964.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0960","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0960.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0642","title":"Multiple Vendors POP Service 未授权访问漏洞","description":"该漏洞条目原描述为目标系统运行了 POP（Post Office Protocol）邮件服务，该服务默认监听 TCP 110 端口。运行 POP 服务本身并不构成直接安全漏洞，但在配置不当（如未启用加密、使用弱口令认证、暴露于公网）的情况下，远程攻击者可能通过暴力破解或会话劫持等方式获取邮件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该条目已被 CVE 官方驳回，认为其属于通用配置枚举（CCE）范畴而非安全漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0642"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.973","remediation":"如非业务必需，建议在服务器上禁用 POP3 服务（如 CentOS: `systemctl disable dovecot`；Ubuntu: `systemctl disable pop3`）；如确需使用，限制仅允许加密连接（启用 TLS/SSL，设置 `ssl = required`），并在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信 IP 访问 TCP 端口 110。同时建议使用 IMAPS（端口 993）替代明文 POP3。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0642","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0960.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0958","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0958.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0641","title":"Multiple Unix UUCP 服务远程安全漏洞","description":"UUCP（Unix-to-Unix Copy Protocol）服务默认在 TCP 端口 540 上运行，该服务设计上缺乏充分的身份认证机制，远程攻击者可在无需认证的情况下通过 UUCP 协议与目标系统建立连接，执行文件传输、远程命令执行等操作，导致系统被未授权访问。该问题影响早期运行 UUCP 服务的多种 Unix 系统，攻击者利用此服务可窃取敏感文件或控制系统，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0641"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.627","remediation":"立即停止并禁用 UUCP 服务（uucp/uucico），执行 `systemctl stop uucp && systemctl disable uucp`（或对应 init 脚本 `service uucp stop && chkconfig uucp off`）。如业务必须使用，应配置 TCP Wrapper（/etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny）限制可信来源 IP，并在防火墙上关闭 TCP 540 端口。若无需 UUCP 功能，建议直接卸载 uucp 软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0641","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0641","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0641.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5v9j-2mwh-j984/GHSA-5v9j-2mwh-j984.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0958.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0956","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0956.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0640","title":"Gopher 服务远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"Unix 系统中 Gopher 服务（默认端口 70）被启用时，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该协议的文件检索功能探测系统目录结构、访问敏感文件，或结合其他服务漏洞实施进一步渗透攻击。该漏洞影响所有运行 Gopher 服务的 Unix 系统，攻击难度低且无需用户交互，严重威胁信息安全。建议关闭不使用的 Gopher 服务以减少攻击面。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0640"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.513","remediation":"立即停止运行 Gopher 服务，并从服务管理器禁用开机自启。若业务无需使用 Gopher 协议，建议彻底卸载 gopherd 软件包；如有历史数据兼容需求，可在防火墙层面封禁 TCP 端口 70 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0640","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0640.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0640","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0640.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0640.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0640.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-84x2-992j-4cgr/GHSA-84x2-992j-4cgr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0640.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0f3e5505-8487-4fbd-876c-46c388a9795c.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7ae10c2036875bb5ef530e18322e7ca2477ed16c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0956.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0954","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0954.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0639","title":"Unix Chargen 服务反射放大拒绝服务漏洞","description":"chargen（字符生成）服务是一种过时的网络诊断协议，默认监听 TCP/UDP 19 端口，在接收到连接请求后会持续输出大量字符数据。攻击者可通过伪造源 IP 地址向目标系统的 UDP chargen 服务发送小数据包，利用服务放大响应流量实施分布式拒绝服务（DDoS）攻击。此外，该服务无需认证即可访问，可能导致信息泄露和服务滥用。该问题属于安全配置缺陷，影响 Unix/Linux 及部分 Windows 系统中默认启用 inetd 的版本。修复措施为在 inetd 配置中禁用 chargen 服务（注释掉 /etc/inetd.conf 中相关行）或使用防火墙阻止外部对 19 端口的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0639"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.383","remediation":"在 Unix/Linux 系统中，编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 文件，注释或删除 chargen 相关行（如 chargen stream tcp nowait root internal），然后重启 inetd 服务（`kill -HUP <inetd_pid>`）。在 Windows 系统中，通过「服务」管理器禁用 \"Simple TCP/IP Services\" 或 \"Character Generator\" 服务。该服务为过时诊断协议，无业务依赖时应彻底禁用，防止被用于 UDP/TCP 反射放大攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0639","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0639.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0639","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0639.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0954.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0948","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0636","title":"多厂商 Discard 服务安全配置漏洞","description":"Discard 服务（RFC 863，TCP/UDP 端口 9）是一种诊断网络服务，收到所有数据后直接丢弃而不做任何处理。该服务在生产环境中启用会无谓增加系统攻击面，攻击者可通过端口扫描发现该服务并确认主机存活，用于网络侦察；在 UDP 模式下，还可被用于反射放大 DDoS 攻击的流量放大链，导致目标网络带宽耗尽。此外，大量向该服务发送数据包可能造成服务器资源消耗。该漏洞无需认证、可远程利用，影响所有启用了 discard 服务的系统，应关闭该服务或通过防火墙限制访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0636"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.037","remediation":"在 Linux/Unix 中编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 discard 相关行（stream 和 dgram）并重启 inetd 服务；systemd 系统执行 systemctl mask discard.socket 停止并屏蔽 discard socket。Windows 系统通过控制面板取消勾选\"简单 TCP/IP 服务\"或运行 dism /online /disable-feature /featurename:SimpleTCP 卸载。同时建议在防火墙上阻断 TCP 和 UDP 端口 9 的入站流量，并检查禁用 echo（端口 7）、chargen（端口 19）等类似高危服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0636.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/SHN_discard.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--78c74f51-06af-4c13-a78e-77284614fcad.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0946","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0946.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0635","title":"多种操作系统 Echo 服务运行反射放大拒绝服务漏洞","description":"回声服务（Echo Service）运行于 TCP/UDP 端口 7，该服务将接收到的任意数据原样返回给发送方。攻击者可利用此服务进行信息收集，探测目标系统存活状态；更严重的是，攻击者可伪造源地址利用 UDP 回声服务发起反射放大型拒绝服务攻击，大量响应数据包会涌向被伪造的目标地址，导致目标带宽或资源耗尽。该漏洞影响默认开启该服务的所有旧版本操作系统。修复建议为禁用回声服务或通过防火墙阻止外部对端口 7 的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0635"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.917","remediation":"立即禁用回声服务（echo service）：在 Unix/Linux 系统中注释 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中的 echo 行并重启 inetd，或执行 `systemctl disable echo-dgram echo-stream` 禁用 systemd socket；在 Windows 系统中通过服务管理器停止并禁用 Simple TCP/IP Services 或使用 `sc stop echo` 命令。同时在边界防火墙上封禁 UDP/TCP 7 端口以防止反射放大攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lists.grok.org.uk/pipermail/full-disclosure/2006-January/041434.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/18514","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0635.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0635","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0635.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/echo.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2009/echo_udp.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0946.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0945","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0945.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0634","title":"SSH 服务运行配置暴露","description":"CVE-1999-0634 已被拒绝使用。该编号原用于描述\"SSH 服务正在运行\"这一配置状态，但经评估该条目并非直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷，而属于安全配置管理范畴。此类配置项更适合纳入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系进行管理，因此 CVE 编号委员会决定拒绝此编号。该问题不涉及具体的攻击方法、漏洞原理或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0634"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.870","remediation":"评估 SSH 服务是否必需，非必需则关闭 sshd 服务（systemctl disable sshd）；如需保留，配置密钥认证登录、禁用 root 直接登录（PermitRootLogin no）、修改默认端口 22 为高编号端口、限制来源 IP（hosts.allow/iptables），并保持 OpenSSH 为最新稳定版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0634","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/lymwhen/lymwhen.github.io/blob/b77540924df6be1e7c614e34dd724374affd2cbf/Linux/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D.md","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/thoraf20/vulnscan/blob/600477d061ab5462099630f9f0924cc5383c5452/network.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0945.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0943","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0943.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0633","title":"HTTP/WWW 服务运行配置检查项（非漏洞）","description":"CVE-1999-0633 已被官方驳回（REJECT），原候选编号指向\"HTTP/WWW 服务正在运行\"这一配置检测项。该条目涉及的是系统上 HTTP 服务端口的开放状态识别，并非安全漏洞，不具备攻击条件和利用方式，不产生 CVSS 评分。此类配置检查更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系，而非 CVE 漏洞编号体系。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0633"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.750","remediation":"若 HTTP 服务非业务必需，应在系统服务管理器中禁用 httpd/nginx/IIS 等相关服务并配置防火墙阻止 80/443 端口入站流量；若为业务必要，应确保移除默认页面、禁用目录列表、限制访问来源 IP、启用 TLS 并定期更新 Web 服务器至最新稳定版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0633","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/HTTP%20index.html%20check.plugin","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000461.txt","https://github.com/lymwhen/lymwhen.github.io/blob/b77540924df6be1e7c614e34dd724374affd2cbf/Linux/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D.md","https://github.com/Planet-Source-Code/marc-ruef-attack-tool-kit-4-0__1-58262/blob/47bd1012c1edf591e9c9fe874122b617137e1b87/atk-4.0src/plugins/HTTP%20404%20enumeration.plugin","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/low/%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87HTTP%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E8%BF%9C%E7%AB%AFWWW%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0943.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0939","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0939.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0632","title":"通用 RPC Portmapper 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"系统运行了 RPC 端口映射服务（rpcbind），该服务会向远程查询者暴露主机上运行的所有 RPC 服务的程序号、版本号和端口号。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该服务收集系统上运行的 RPC 服务清单，从而获取目标系统信息以辅助进一步攻击，构成信息泄露风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0632"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.710","remediation":"在网络边界防火墙上阻止 TCP/UDP 111 端口的入站流量，防止外部枚举 RPC 服务。如业务不需要 RPC 服务，可禁用 portmap/rpcbind 服务（Linux 上执行 `systemctl disable rpcbind && systemctl stop rpcbind`）；若需使用，应限制仅信任来源 IP 可访问，避免暴露在公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0632","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0632","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f06304a9243ce013bfbf7cea427539f6409c0a05/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0632.md","https://github.com/packetchaos/navi/blob/48d4e8df93f0f87e8654f6bfb01844b5dea4ed58/Queries.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/rpc_portmap.nasl","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/defenxor/dsiem/blob/a436146a07576ac81c0b2e02afb7b5e88114951b/internal/pkg/plugin/nesd/fixtures/nessus_example.csv","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_portmap_port32771.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0939.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0937","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0937.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0631","title":"NFS 服务未授权访问配置问题","description":"该漏洞为已被撤销的 CVE 编号，原指 NFS（网络文件系统）服务在目标主机上处于运行状态。NFS 服务默认监听 TCP/UDP 2049 端口，若未配置严格的访问控制策略（如 exports 权限限制、IP 过滤、认证机制），远程未授权攻击者可通过网络探测到该服务，进而可能尝试挂载或访问导出的文件系统，导致敏感文件泄露或进一步渗透。该问题不属于安全漏洞范畴，已被转移至通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理，CVSS 评分 0.0，不涉及具体的攻击利用链路或需修复的软件缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0631"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.713","remediation":"如非业务需要，应在不需要 NFS 共享的服务器上关闭 NFS 服务（systemctl disable nfs-server）；确需使用时，应限制 exports 仅允许特定 IP 段访问并使用 root_squash 选项，同时在防火墙中限制 2049/TCP 端口仅对受信来源开放，推荐启用 NFSv4 及以上版本并禁用 NFSv2/v3","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0631","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0937.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0932","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0932.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0629","title":"通用 ident/identd 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"ident/identd 服务（RFC 1413）运行时会监听 113 端口，为任何 TCP 连接请求返回对应进程的拥有者用户名。未经授权的远程攻击者可利用该服务枚举系统上的用户账户信息，为后续暴力破解或针对性攻击提供侦察支持。虽然该服务本身不直接导致代码执行，但其暴露的用户信息会降低系统安全防护等级，属于信息泄露风险。建议在非必要情况下禁用该服务或通过防火墙限制对 113 端口的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0629"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.460","remediation":"建议立即停止 identd 服务并禁用其开机自启：在 Linux 系统中执行 `systemctl stop identd && systemctl disable identd`（或 `service identd stop && chkconfig identd off`）；在 Cisco IOS 上执行 `no service tcp-small-servers`。同时通过防火墙屏蔽 TCP 端口 113，阻止外部访问该服务。如无业务依赖，应彻底卸载 identd 软件包（如 `apt-get remove identd`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0629","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0629.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0629","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0629.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/JakeVincet/nvt/blob/f39b9cba98d614dd2a567b15cce1a5eeb97ad782/auth_enabled.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0932.toml"}]